snippet.title: Old Site Release Trailer [PICO-8 Game]
snippet.description:
Old Site is a Celeste Classic mod which adds ideas from the second chapter of the full release of Celeste Classic, Celeste.

You can play it on itch.io here: https://amegpo.itch.io/old-site

You can see more games by me here: https://amegpo.itch.io/
